'''天巡网''' ({{lang-en|Skyscanner}})是全球機票、飯店、租車服務的免費比價[[搜尋引擎|搜尋引擎]]，並提供30種以上的多語言服務<ref>{{cite news|url=http://techcrunch.com/2012/09/18/skyscanners-mobile-apps-hit-10m-downloads-letting-users-find-cheap-flights-on-the-go/|title=Skyscanner’s Mobile Apps Hit 10M Downloads, Letting Users Find Cheap Flights On The Go|last=O'Hear|first=Steve|date=18 September 2012|work=TechCrunch|accessdate=15 May 2011|archive-date=2015-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150912231743/http://techcrunch.com/2012/09/18/skyscanners-mobile-apps-hit-10m-downloads-letting-users-find-cheap-flights-on-the-go/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包括[[中文|中文]]、[[俄文|俄文]]、[[葡萄牙語|葡萄牙語]]等等。在Skyscanner平台上，並不直接銷售機票，而是讓用戶尋找到最便宜的交易後，引導用戶到航空公司、租車公司、飯店、或是旅行社完成訂購程序<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.skyscanner.net/news/ |title=Skyscanner News and Tips |accessdate=2015-09-14 |archive-date=2015-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150915053333/http://www.skyscanner.net/news |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
2001年三位[[資訊科技|資訊科技]]的專業人員：Gareth Williams、Barry Smith與Bonamy Grime共同组成。（在他們之中的一人因為在搜索滑雪勝地的便宜機票面臨了重重的困難之後。）2002年发布的第一個版本上線。2003年公司聘用的第一位員工，協助網站的開發。2004年愛丁堡的總部建立<ref>Butcher, Mike (17 January 2011). [http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-scotland-business-21318799 Flight firm Skyscanner moves in to America] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-scotland-business-21318799 |date=20160105021216 }}, Tech Crunch. Retrieved 15 May 2011.</ref>。一開始網站上只列出歐洲的[[廉價航空|廉價航空]]，不過也很快地擴展搜索範圍到傳統航空，如[[英國航空|英國航空]]、[[荷蘭皇家航空|荷蘭皇家航空]]、[[維珍航空|維珍航空]]等等。之後，也擴張的搜尋的地理版圖到美國、加拿大、亞洲以及世界各地。2011年收購了Door-to-door的旅遊網站Zoombu，不過不願透漏價格<ref>[http://techcrunch.com/2011/01/17/travel-search-engine-skyscanner-acquires-zoombu/ Travel search engine Skyscanner acquires Zoombu] {{Wayback|url=http://techcrunch.com/2011/01/17/travel-search-engine-skyscanner-acquires-zoombu/ |date=20160304082736 }}, techcrunch, Jan 17, 2011.</ref>。2011年9月，Skyscanner在[[新加坡|新加坡]]設立了辦公室，做為亞太地區的營運總部<ref>[http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-scotland-business-13919093 Skyscanner to set up operation in Singapore] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-scotland-business-13919093 |date=20140726112311 }}, BBC. 26 June 2011.</ref>。2012年北京辦公室啟用，並與中國最大的搜尋引擎─[[百度|百度]]建立合夥關係<ref>[http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-scotland-business-19358227 Skyscanner lands China search engine deal] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-scotland-business-19358227 |date=20160105024632 }}, BBC. 23 August 2012.</ref>。2013年2月宣布將在美國[[邁阿密|邁阿密]]建立據點的計畫<ref>[http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-scotland-business-21318799 Flight firm Skyscanner moves in to America] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-scotland-business-21318799 |date=20160105021216 }}, BBC. 4 February 2012 .</ref>。2013年10月[[紅杉資本|紅杉資本]]宣布入股，並持有約8億美金的股份<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.standard.co.uk/business/business-news/skyscanner-valued-at-800m-by-backer-of-apple-8855825.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-02-25 |archive-date=2016-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302091939/http://www.standard.co.uk/business/business-news/skyscanner-valued-at-800m-by-backer-of-apple-8855825.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>（到2013年已經聘用了超過180名以上的員工）。2014年6月收購中國大陸的旅遊搜尋引擎Youbibi<ref>[http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-scotland-business-28014913 Skyscanner buys Chinese metasearch firm Youbibi] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-scotland-business-28014913 |date=20160105021901 }}, BBC. 25 June 2014 .</ref>。2014年8月根據一份行銷研究指出，相較於其他的旅遊網站，其使用者主要介於16-34歲之間，而所有的使用者中，有64%認為其是個可信任的平台<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ljresearch.co.uk/tripadvisor-tops-travel-brand-awareness-index/ |title=TripAdvisor tops Travel Brand Awareness Index |accessdate=2016-02-25 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303224139/http://www.ljresearch.co.uk/tripadvisor-tops-travel-brand-awareness-index/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年10月收購了位於布達佩斯的行動程式開發商Distinction<ref>[http://techcrunch.com/2014/10/22/travel-search-company-skyscanner-acquires-budapest-based-mobile-app-developer-distinction/ Travel Search Company Skyscanner Acquires Budapest-Based Mobile App Developer Distinction] {{Wayback|url=http://techcrunch.com/2014/10/22/travel-search-company-skyscanner-acquires-budapest-based-mobile-app-developer-distinction/ |date=20160304055608 }}, techcrunch, Oct 22, 2014.</ref>。2016年1月宣布在國際擴張的過程中，募集了1億9200萬美金<ref>[http://techcrunch.com/2016/01/12/skyscanner-unicorn/ Travel Search Site Skyscanner Raises $192M For International Expansion] {{Wayback|url=http://techcrunch.com/2016/01/12/skyscanner-unicorn/ |date=20160223174219 }}, techcrunch, Jan 12, 2016.</ref>。2016年11月24日，[[攜程旅行網|攜程旅行網]]以14億英鎊（約135億港元）現金将這個全球大型的旅遊搜尋平台之一收购<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/42009/chinas-largest-travel-site-to-buy-skyscanner|title=中國大陸最大旅遊網站攜程宣布以14億英鎊收購Skyscanner|author=張庭瑜|date=2016年11月24日|publisher=數位時代|accessdate=2017年2月13日|archive-date=2017年2月14日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170214002523/https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/42009/chinas-largest-travel-site-to-buy-skyscanner|dead-url=no}}</ref>（中譯名：天巡網）。

== 市場狀況 ==
Skyscanner 目前每個月會有5000萬以上的造訪人次<ref>[http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-scotland-business-35289861 Travel firm Skyscanner secures major investment] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-scotland-business-35289861 |date=20160323113529 }}, BBC, 12 January 2016</ref>，並有9300萬英鎊的年營業額<ref>[http://techcrunch.com/2012/09/18/skyscanners-mobile-apps-hit-10m-downloads-letting-users-find-cheap-flights-on-the-go/] {{Wayback|url=http://techcrunch.com/2012/09/18/skyscanners-mobile-apps-hit-10m-downloads-letting-users-find-cheap-flights-on-the-go/ |date=20150912231743 }}, techcrunch, Sep 18, 2012.</ref>。Skyscanner也獲得了許多不同的獎項，如：{{link-en|女王企業獎|Queen's Award for Enterprise}}、2011年年度旅游品牌（Travolution Brand of the Year 2011）<ref name="#1">[http://www.skyscanner.net/news  "Skyscanner Awards"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.skyscanner.net/news |date=20150915053333 }}, Skyscanner</ref>、以及2010年年度最佳機票比價品牌（Best Flight Comparison 2010 from Travolution）<ref name="#1"/>等。

Skyscanner網站也獲得英國媒體的一致好評。在[[衛報|衛報]]上的一篇名為〈網路廉價航班查找實驗〉（Online Cheap Flight Finding Experiment）的文章中，以「打敗了如[[Expedia|Expedia]]和[[Travelocity|Travelocity]]等更大的營運商」讚譽Skyscanner可以找到最便宜的機票<ref>Brignall, Miles; Patrick Collinson (17 September 2005). [http://www.theguardian.com/money/2005/sep/17/moneysupplement.travel Go online to get a flying start] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theguardian.com/money/2005/sep/17/moneysupplement.travel |date=20160304132920 }}, The Guardian. Retrieved 15 May 2011.</ref>。在[[獨立報|獨立報]]的一篇文章中，Skyscamner也被列為「十大優秀旅遊網站」<ref>[http://www.independent.co.uk/travel/news-and-advice/the-ten-best-travel-websites-486356.html The Ten Best: Travel websites] {{Wayback|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/travel/news-and-advice/the-ten-best-travel-websites-486356.html |date=20160304134522 }}, The Independent. 13 January 2005. Retrieved 15 May 2011.</ref>和「101個真的有用的網站」<ref>Rebecca Armstrong, Rhodri Marsden, Abigail Outhwaite and Jimmy Lee Shreeve (11 June 2007). [http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/features/101-really-useful-websites-452559.html 101 Really Useful Websites] {{Wayback|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/features/101-really-useful-websites-452559.html |date=20160301184944 }}, The Independent. Retrieved 15 May 2011.</ref>。[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]評Skyscanner為「九個最佳旅遊網站之一」<ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/6550711/Best-websites-Travel.html Best websites: Travel] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/6550711/Best-websites-Travel.html |date=20160319133758 }},The Daily Telegraph. 12 November 2009. Retrieved 15 May 2011.</ref>。

旅遊比價的市場急遽成長，也有許多公司提供相似的服務，如[[Kayak.com|Kayak.com]]、[[Dohop|Dohop]]、[[Travelocity|Travelocity]]、[[JetRadar|JetRadar]]、[[Orbitz|Orbitz]]、[[CheapOair|CheapOair]]、以及[[Mobissimo|Mobissimo]]等等。

